{"tid":690002,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"macbook backup 問題","createTime":"2018-06-04T13:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T11:13:35.000Z","uid":107269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"937bf3ea9bf334eb50f4e040c12213a782432ffb","tid":690002,"uid":107269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"你好<br />\n因為我諗住轉會用macbook<br />\n咁我本第用緊window , 亦有一隻外置hdd<br />\n咁我知macbook 讀唔到我隻hdd<br />\n要format 過先得<br />\n<br />\n咁我會將hdd d 野過返入window 機先<br />\n跟住我要將隻hdd format 做乜格式？<br />\n因為format 完之後我要由window 過返落hdd<br />\n目的係macbook 可以正常睇返哂d file<br />\n<br />\n其實詳細format 步驟係點做呢？？<br />\n中間有乜要注意呢？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想請教下為日後方便<br />\n一個完善既backup 應該點樣做呢？<br />\n用乜軟件、乜format, 用幾多隻hdd....之類<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打們明我想問乜<br />\n（因為知識有限，怕問得好怪）<br />\n同埋幫到我啦<br />\n<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"84615dee197409d4ab1e67971511c57d8b09f453","tid":690002,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e778d97a577a2dbe33d41371bcf1ede2f39b6bcb","tid":690002,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"Macbook係手機？"},{"pid":"e09fc09835f5a190e5ba027dc0bfeccc7b426388","tid":690002,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"俾我會用macbook將隻external界兩個partition<br />\n一個HFS+(macOS extended),做time machine<br />\n一個exFAT/FAT擺file,兩邊都用到"},{"pid":"b8c0c7b281759d09733216bf509f2c487e8d9e42","tid":690002,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c07f8cb97aba370c8c196fc7d8d3ddb4ab238018","tid":690002,"uid":107269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09fc09835f5a190e5ba027dc0bfeccc7b426388","tid":690002,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"俾我會用macbook將隻external界兩個partition<br />\n一個HFS+(macOS extended),做time machine<br />\n一個exFAT/FAT擺file,兩邊都用到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"I see I see <br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"db8ae0e7443fd16c28c319738d29b2ff6b013619","tid":690002,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"外置hdd 唔洗format <br />\nmac 可以讀到NTFS 同 FAT"},{"pid":"6ba4bc5052c51c2028bcfc546374664f58e25aa6","tid":690002,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09fc09835f5a190e5ba027dc0bfeccc7b426388","tid":690002,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"俾我會用macbook將隻external界兩個partition<br />\n一個HFS+(macOS extended),做time machine<br />\n一個exFAT/FAT擺file,兩邊都用到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:37:13.000Z","msg":"Hard disk唔好用exfat 冇journaling好易炒"},{"pid":"b26705fa0160e9b53b86a86f140a049c6c8a2dfd","tid":690002,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"1. 隻disk好大舊 唔係一兩年內用得晒，HFS+（正常用） HFS+（Time Machine，大概成部mac嘅1.5倍） NTFS<br />\n2. 隻disk細舊，HFS+（Time Machine） NTFS<br />\n<br />\nNTFS可以用響Mac 裝Monty read/write"},{"pid":"ce83a009890a4790b12a036d87d3968a1f8155cb","tid":690002,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"留意番 time machine要另外𠝹獨立比佢用"},{"pid":"54213179641e2609fc9da51a3c9bc498bae0b656","tid":690002,"uid":11567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"淨係抄資料去macbook唔駛用HDD<br />\n用同一個網絡仲快"},{"pid":"926945299c5481468d859c73bd4e4af40f0a6902","tid":690002,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54213179641e2609fc9da51a3c9bc498bae0b656","tid":690002,"uid":11567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"淨係抄資料去macbook唔駛用HDD<br />\n用同一個網絡仲快"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"我屋企部desktop 裝左 linux 做network drive 同 time machine server<br />\n部macbook 插左電就自已backup"},{"pid":"5191b1fc6622c6a1e